sequenceDiagram
    participant FW
    participant RST as ResetCtrl
    participant PLL
    participant CLK as ClockCtrl
    participant GPU as GPU Domain

    FW->>RST: assert reset
    FW->>PLL: program PLL params and enable
    PLL-->>FW: pll_lock
    FW->>CLK: select PLL clock path
    CLK-->>FW: clock stable / ack
    FW->>RST: deassert reset with sync release
    RST-->>GPU: reset released on stable clock
